<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>La tua Stanza — La Piazza Pulita</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">

    <style>
        body {
            background: black;
            color: #f5f5f5;
            font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", serif;
        }

        .sfondo-stanza {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0; left: 0;
            width: 100%; height: 100%;
            background-image: url('img/nebbia-stanza.png');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            opacity: 0.35;
            filter: blur(4px);
            z-index: -1;
        }

        /* Menu superiore */
        .menu-superiore {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            z-index: 10;
            position: relative;
        }

        .menu-superiore a {
            margin: 0 0.6rem;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            opacity: 0.8;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .menu-superiore a:hover {
            opacity: 1;
            text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
        }

        /* Contenitore */
        .modifica-box {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 4rem auto;
            padding: 2rem;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.55);
            backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
            border-radius: 14px;
        }

        h2 {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px black;
        }

        input, textarea, select {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 0.8rem;
            margin-top: 0.8rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: none;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
            color: white;
        }

        textarea {
            height: 120px;
            resize: none;
        }

        label {
            margin-top: 1.2rem;
            display: block;
            font-weight: bold;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        button {
            margin-top: 2rem;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 0.8rem;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
            color: white;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        button:hover {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
        }

        .nota {
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
            text-align: center;
            opacity: 0.85;
            font-style: italic;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body class="stanza-body">

<div class="sfondo-stanza"></div>

<!-- Menu superiore -->
<div id="menu-container"></div>
<script src="js/menu.js"></script>

<div class="modifica-box">

    <h2>Personalizza la tua Stanza</h2>

    <!-- Versione estetica, senza PHP -->
    <form>

        <input type="text" name="nome_stanza" placeholder="Nome della stanza">

        <textarea name="frase" placeholder="Una frase che ti rappresenta"></textarea>

        <label>Sfondo (immagine):</label>
        <input type="file" name="sfondo">

        <label>Colore dominante:</label>
        <input type="color" name="colore">

        <label>Simbolo:</label>
        <select name="simbolo">
            <option value="lanterna">Lanterna</option>
            <option value="stella">Stella</option>
            <option value="onda">Onda</option>
            <option value="chiave">Chiave</option>
        </select>

        <button type="button">Salva (non attivo)</button>

    </form>

    <p class="nota">
        La tua stanza è il tuo porto.<br>
        Qui puoi renderla come vuoi.
    </p>

</div>

</body>
</html>
